Ici le runtime-test est installé
4 pass ...
~/local/src/tmp/test/antlr4.6/runtime-testsuite$ mvn -e -Dtest=java.TestParserExec test


Ici le runtime est installé sans les test (remove debug=true)
~/local/src/tmp/antlr4.6$ mvn -DskipTests install


generate test report :

$> cd antlr/tests
$> gtester test_libantlr -o=test_libantlr.xml
$> echo "Add <info> in test_libantlr.xml"

<?xml version="1.0"?>
<gtester>
<info>
<package>PACKAGENAME</package>
<version>VERSION</version>
<revision>REVISION</revision>
</info>

...
</gtester>

$> gtester-report tests_libantlr.xml > tests_libantlr.html
